channel.title: Latest Post on Fapesoft
channel.description: Recent content in Latest Post on Fapesoft

item.title: Always listen to users
item.description: It has now been 5 months since I launched would you rather app, until now the app that has received the most downloads and use by users, things are turning in the right direction.

item.title: At the cinema they make a movie with the shark, that's cool
item.description: I came out of the cinema, after seeing a beautiful movie with a shark. I’ve always seen sharks as the kings of the seas.

item.title: Follow your passions
item.description: One of my greatest passions are animals. I love going to the zoo when I can, and I love to see the documents that portray moments of life in nature.

item.title: I still have a passion for useful apps
item.description: All mobile app developers believe at least once in their life they have made, or at least thought about developing a flashlight app.

item.title: It all starts here
item.description: A normal day, a normal guy, these are the ingredients that pushed me to start. If you start you are already halfway through the work I thought, then why not try it?

item.title: Replica
item.description: I’m still excited about the launch of my previous Animal sound app. I think it can be really useful to someone.

item.title: Something more
item.description: We are always playing the same games. I want something more, I want to evolve my skills. Why not develop something multiplayer?

item.title: Thanks The Boring Flutter Development Show
item.description: A day like any other spent watching The Boring Flutter Development Show. Suddenly they begin to implement a beautiful watch, with a fantastic effect.

item.title: The unexpected events of life
item.description: Just when I was going right, life comes before me. A really difficult year from the point of view of my emotions, I had serious losses and moments of despair that took me away from my second hobby (the first will always remain the love for family and for relationships with people dear to me.

item.title: This is not the time to give up
item.description: 8 months without continuing with what I like to do, the apps. Studying at university and family commitments did not allow me to pursue my hobbies, ahhh serious mistake.

item.title: We are eternal children
item.description: We are eternal children, we have fun with simple things, and perhaps this is also the meaning of life. The best thing in life is to give a smile, it costs you nothing to do it.

item.title: Yes, but something useful?
item.description: So far I have only made games. I would like to do something more useful. Something that people can use relamente, which can serve in everyday life.
